name: "IT'S A MEME!"
description:
As the name "meme" suggests, it's not always an original art just like many of the Pepe memes that are either based on classic european/asian/etc paintings or are based on scenes of movies/animations...

I have reproduced the original with my own additions as a meme!

"100% of the profit will be donated to the original artist (Tony Sart)"
